'''RH Mining Corporation''' was a large [[Mining/Legends|mining]] corporation that existed during the final years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. RH Mining was formed by [[Rees Haslip]] but was later inherited by his daughter, [[Keriin Haslip]], upon his death. Keriin sold the corporation to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]], who presumably nationalized it.

